snippet.title: Dragon Nest 2: Evolution| Pre-registration Now Available!
snippet.description:
Dare to discover dragons together!

【Dragon Nest 2: Evolution】, the free-to-play MMORPG is now open for global pre-registration, paving the way for new players to be part of the epic fantasy adventure that has already been experienced by over 300 million players to date.

---

Great adventurers! You have heard the whispering call of the goddess Altea, please come back and continue to write your faith and mission together!  #DragonNest2 #DN2 

You can also find us on: 
Global :
